  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Iterable<Point3D>, java.util.Collection<Point3D>, java.util.Deque<Point3D>, java.util.List<Point3D>, java.util.Queue<Point3D>

    public class Path
extends java.util.LinkedList<Point3D>
    This class represents a path that contains a collection of 3D points that this path is created for each Pacman in the game. In addition to this class it is possible to calculate for each time point where the pecman was.
    Author:
    Netanel, Carmel
